annotationA: Ribosomal protein L22-like is a eukaryotic-specific component of the large ribosomal subunit involved in protein synthesis
annotationB: 60S ribosomal protein L19; Structural constituent of ribosome. It is involved in the biological process described with: centrosome duplication; mitotic spindle elongation; translation; Belongs to the eukaryotic ribosomal protein eL19 family
